message.content:
Ecco una landing page single-file in stile cyberpunk per un negozio di programmazione AI, con modulo contatti e popup di conferma.

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>AI Code Emporium • Cyberpunk</title>
    <!-- Font futuristico -->
    <link href="https://https" rel="stylesheet" href="https.com/integrazione.2" crossorigin>
    <style>
    /* Reset e strade cyberpunk */
    * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
        background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, #0d0d14 0%, #1200 100%, #0 100%);
        background-color: #0a0a0f;
        font-family: 'Orpo', 'Couro', monospace;
        color: #f0f0f0;
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 20px;
        margin: 0;
        background-image: 
            repeating-linear-gradient(0deg, rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.1) 1px, transparent 1px),
            repeating-linear-gradient(0deg, rgba(255, 0, 255, 0.1) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 4px 4px;
    animation: scan 8s linear infinite;
    @keyframes scan {
    0% { background-position: 0 0; }
    100% { background-position: 0 40px; }
    }
    /* overlay gruglia */
    body::before {
        content: '';
        position: fixed;
        top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
        background: repeating-linear-gradient(0deg, rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.1) 1px, transparent 1px);
        pointer-events: none;
        z-index: 0;
    }

    .card {
        background: #0e0e0e;
        border: 2px solid #0ff;
        box-shadow: 0 0 20px #0ff8, 0 0 40px #f0f, inset 0 0 20px #0ff4;
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 2rem 2rem 2rem;
        max-width: 520px;
        width: 100%;
        backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
        position: relative;
    z-index: 10;
    transition: box-shadow 0.2s;
    }
    .card:hover {
        box-shadow: 0 0 30px #0ff, 0 0 60px #f0f, inset 0 0 30px #0ff;
    }

    h1 {
        font-size: 2.4rem;
        text-align: center;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing:  -0.2em;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        text-shadow: 0 0 10px #0ff, 0 0 20px #f0f, 0 0 30px #00f;
        color: #fff;
        font-weight: 700;
    }

    .s-sub {
        display: block;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: #0ff;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f4;
        padding-bottom: 0.8rem;
        text-shadow: 0 0 5px #0ff;
    }

    .grid {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1.2rem;
    }

    .input-group {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 0.3rem;
    }

    label {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
        color: #f0f;
        text-shadow: 0 0 5px #f0f;
    }

    input, textarea {
        background: #0a0a0f;
        border: 1px solid #0ff;
        border-radius: 4px;
        padding: 0.8rem 0.6rem;
        font-family: 'Orpo', monospace;
        color: #fff;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        outline: none;
        transition: border 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
        box-shadow: 0 0 5px transparent;
    }
    input:focus, textarea:focus {
        border-color: #f0f;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px #0ff, 0 0 10px #f0f;
    }

    textarea {
        resize: vertical;
        min-height: 80px;
    }

    button {
        background: #0a0a0f;
        border: 2px solid #0ff;
        color: #0ff;
        padding: 0.8rem 1.2rem;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 2px;
        font-weight: bold;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: all 0.2s;
        box-shadow: 0 0 5px #0ff, 0 0 10px transparent;
        margin-top: 0.2rem;
        width: 100%;
    }
    button:hover {
        background: #0ff;
        color: #0a0a0f;
        box-shadow: 0 0 20px #0ff, 0 0 40px #f0f;
        border-color: #f0f;
    }

    .footer {
        margin-top: 2rem;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 0.7rem;
        color: #888;
        border-top: 1px solid #f0f3;
        padding-top: 1rem;
    }

    .footer a {
        color: #0ff;
        text-decoration: none;
    }

    .popup-over {
        display: none;
        position: fixed;
        top: 0; left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
        backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
        z-index: 1000;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        animation: fade 0.3s;
    }
    .popup-over.show {
        display: flex;
    }

    .popup-box {
        background: #0e0e0e;
        border: 2px solid #0ff;
        box-shadow: 0 0 20px #0ff, 0 0 40px #f0f;
        padding: 2rem 3rem;
        border-radius: 12px;
        text-align: center;
    }
    .popup-box h2 {
        font-size: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .popup-box p {
        color: #0ff;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .popup-box .close {
        background: transparent;
        border: 1px solid #f0f;
        color: #f0f;
        padding: 0.5rem 2rem;
        cursor: pointer;
        font-size: 1rem;
        transition: 0.2s;
    }
    .popup-box .close:hover {
        background: #f0f;
        color: #0a0a0f;
    }

    .error-m {
        color: #f0f;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        margin-top: 0.2rem;
    }
    .hidden {
        display: none;
    }
</style>
